                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Email Us</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
                                    For general inquiries and support
